<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Earendil Advisory — Internal Pitch</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,500&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --navy:  #0a1628;
    --navy2: #0f1f3a;
    --gold:  #c4a359;
    --gold2: #e2c47a;
    --cream: #e8dfc8;
    --muted: #8a9ab5;
    --white: #f5f2ec;
  }

  html, body {
    background: #06101e;
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    color: var(--cream);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  .deck {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3px;
    padding: 24px 12px 60px;
  }

  .slide {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 900px;
    background: var(--navy);
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: min(100svh, 560px);
  }

  .horizon {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 54px; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, var(--gold) 15%, var(--gold) 85%, transparent 100%);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .slide-footer {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 16px; left: 32px; right: 32px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .footer-logo {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    color: var(--muted); font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .content {
    flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 48px 48px 90px;
    gap: 0;
  }

  h1 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.05; color: var(--white); }
  h2 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: var(--white); }
  .gold { color: var(--gold); }
  .italic { font-style: italic; }
  p, .body { font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: var(--cream); line-height: 1.65; }

  /* ── LOGO FOOTER SNIPPET ── */
  .logo-footer-svg { opacity: 0.5; }

  /* ══ SLIDE 1: TITLE ══ */
  .s1 .starfield { position: absolute; inset: 0; overflow: hidden; pointer-events: none; }
  .s1 .starfield::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 12% 18%, rgba(196,163,89,0.6) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 78%  9%, rgba(232,223,200,0.4) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 55% 25%, rgba(196,163,89,0.5) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 88% 35%, rgba(232,223,200,0.3) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 33% 55%, rgba(232,223,200,0.25) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 67% 70%, rgba(196,163,89,0.3) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 22% 82%, rgba(232,223,200,0.2) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 91% 88%, rgba(232,223,200,0.3) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at  5% 44%, rgba(232,223,200,0.2) 0%, transparent 100%);
  }
  .s1 .content {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    align-items: center; text-align: center;
    gap: 28px; padding-top: 60px;
  }
  .s1 .title-logo-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 24px; }
  .s1 h1 { font-size: clamp(56px, 10vw, 88px); letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .s1 .subtitle {
    font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted); max-width: 340px; line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ══ SLIDE 2: THE MYTH ══ */
  .s2-myth .content { gap: 32px; }
  .s2-myth h2 { font-size: clamp(30px, 5vw, 52px); max-width: 700px; }
  .s2-myth .myth-body {
    font-size: 15px; color: var(--muted); max-width: 640px; line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .s2-myth .myth-quote {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic; font-size: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 24px);
    color: var(--gold); border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
    padding-left: 24px; max-width: 620px; line-height: 1.5;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  /* ══ SLIDE 3: PREMISE ══ */
  .s3 .content { gap: 28px; }
  .s3 h2 { font-size: clamp(30px, 5vw, 50px); }
  .s3 p  { font-size: 15px; max-width: 600px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 8px; }

  /* ══ SLIDE 4: THE FIRM ══ */
  .s4-firm .content { gap: 36px; }
  .s4-firm h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 46px); }
  .s4-firm .pillars { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 0; margin-top: 8px; }
  .s4-firm .pillar {
    padding: 22px 24px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(196,163,89,0.25);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;
  }
  .s4-firm .pillar + .pillar { border-left: 1px solid rgba(196,163,89,0.1); }
  .s4-firm .pillar-title { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); }
  .s4-firm .pillar-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ══ SLIDE 5: TARGET CLIENT ══ */
  .s5-client .content { gap: 36px; }
  .s5-client h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 46px); max-width: 600px; }
  .s5-client .client-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; max-width: 720px; }
  .s5-client .client-card {
    padding: 24px; background: rgba(196,163,89,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196,163,89,0.15);
  }
  .s5-client .client-title { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .s5-client .client-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

  /* ══ SLIDE 6: SERVICES ══ */
  .s6-svc .content { gap: 36px; }
  .s6-svc h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 44px); }
  .s6-svc .svc-row { display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-width: 720px; }
  .s6-svc .svc-item {
    display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 20px;
    padding: 16px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(138,154,181,0.15);
  }
  .s6-svc .svc-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .s6-svc .svc-num { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--gold); width: 36px; flex-shrink: 0; line-height: 1; }
  .s6-svc .svc-content { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .s6-svc .svc-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .s6-svc .svc-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.55; }

  /* ══ SLIDE 7: DIFFERENTIATOR ══ */
  .s7-diff .split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; flex: 1; min-height: 0; }
  .s7-diff .col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 48px; gap: 16px; padding-bottom: 90px; }
  .s7-diff .col-right { border-left: 1px solid rgba(196,163,89,0.2); background: rgba(196,163,89,0.03); }
  .s7-diff .col-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .s7-diff .col-label.bad  { color: var(--muted); }
  .s7-diff .col-label.good { color: var(--gold); }
  .s7-diff h2 { font-size: clamp(22px, 3.5vw, 36px); line-height: 1.2; }
  .s7-diff p  { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; }

  /* ══ SLIDE 8: SILMARIL WHAT IT IS ══ */
  .s8-sil .content { gap: 32px; }
  .s8-sil h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 46px); }
  .s8-sil .sil-intro { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); max-width: 580px; margin-top: -8px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .s8-sil .split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0; }
  .s8-sil .col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; padding: 0 24px 0 0; }
  .s8-sil .col + .col { padding: 0 0 0 24px; border-left: 1px solid rgba(196,163,89,0.2); }
  .s8-sil .list-item { display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .s8-sil .list-marker { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.35; flex-shrink: 0; width: 18px; }
  .s8-sil .list-marker.x     { color: var(--muted); opacity: 0.5; }
  .s8-sil .list-marker.check { color: var(--gold); }
  .s8-sil .list-text { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.55; }
  .s8-sil .list-text.dim { color: var(--muted); }
  .s8-sil .list-text.lit { color: var(--cream); }
  .s8-sil .col-eyebrow { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .s8-sil .col-eyebrow.bad  { color: var(--muted); }
  .s8-sil .col-eyebrow.good { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ══ SLIDE 9: THE MOAT ══ */
  .s9 .content { gap: 36px; }
  .s9 h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 46px); max-width: 560px; }
  .s9 .moat-row { display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-width: 720px; }
  .s9 .moat-item { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 20px; padding: 15px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(138,154,181,0.15); }
  .s9 .moat-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .s9 .moat-marker { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--gold); width: 32px; flex-shrink: 0; line-height: 1; }
  .s9 .moat-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--cream); line-height: 1.55; }
  .s9 .moat-text strong { color: var(--white); font-weight: 500; }

  /* ══ SLIDE 10: PRECEDENTS ══ */
  .s10 .content { gap: 36px; }
  .s10 h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 44px); }
  .s10 .cases { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 32px; }
  .s10 .case-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(196,163,89,0.3); padding-top: 18px; }
  .s10 .case-name { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); }
  .s10 .case-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

  /* ══ SLIDE 11: TEAM ══ */
  .s11 .content { gap: 36px; }
  .s11 h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 44px); }
  .s11 .team-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 0; }
  .s11 .team-member { padding: 24px 28px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(196,163,89,0.25); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .s11 .team-member + .team-member { border-left: 1px solid rgba(196,163,89,0.1); }
  .s11 .member-name { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--white); }
  .s11 .member-role { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); }
  .s11 .member-bio { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ══ SLIDE 12: ROADMAP ══ */
  .s12 .content { gap: 36px; }
  .s12 h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 46px); }
  .s12 .phases { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 0; }
  .s12 .phase { padding: 24px 28px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(196,163,89,0.25); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .s12 .phase + .phase { border-left: 1px solid rgba(196,163,89,0.1); }
  .s12 .phase.active { background: rgba(196,163,89,0.05); border-top-color: var(--gold); }
  .s12 .phase-num { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(196,163,89,0.35); line-height: 1; }
  .s12 .phase.active .phase-num { color: var(--gold); }
  .s12 .phase-title { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); }
  .s12 .phase.active .phase-title { color: var(--gold2); }
  .s12 .phase-timeline { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(196,163,89,0.5); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .s12 .phase-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
  .s12 .phase.active .phase-body { color: var(--cream); }

  /* ══ SLIDE 13: THE ASK ══ */
  .s13 .starfield { position: absolute; inset: 0; overflow: hidden; pointer-events: none; }
  .s13 .starfield::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at  8% 12%, rgba(196,163,89,0.5) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 82%  8%, rgba(232,223,200,0.35) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 60% 20%, rgba(196,163,89,0.4) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 25% 65%, rgba(232,223,200,0.2) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 92% 55%, rgba(196,163,89,0.25) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 47% 85%, rgba(232,223,200,0.2) 0%, transparent 100%);
  }
  .s13 .logo-watermark { position: absolute; right: -30px; bottom: 60px; opacity: 0.04; pointer-events: none; z-index: 1; }
  .s13 .content { position: relative; z-index: 2; gap: 28px; justify-content: center; }
  .s13 h2 { font-size: clamp(30px, 5vw, 56px); max-width: 660px; line-height: 1.1; }
  .s13 .asks { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; max-width: 620px; }
  .s13 .ask-item { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .s13 .ask-bullet { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gold); margin-top: 9px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .s13 .ask-text { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--cream); line-height: 1.6; }
  .s13 .closing { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 20px; color: var(--gold); margin-top: 8px; }

  /* ══ MOBILE ══ */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .deck { padding: 8px 0 40px; gap: 2px; }
    .slide { min-height: auto; }
    .content { padding: 36px 24px 80px; }
    .s1 .content { padding-top: 48px; }
    .s7-diff .split, .s8-sil .split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .s7-diff .col, .s8-sil .col { padding: 32px 24px; padding-bottom: 16px; }
    .s7-diff .col-right { border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(196,163,89,0.2); padding-bottom: 80px; }
    .s8-sil .col + .col { border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(196,163,89,0.15); padding: 24px 0 0; }
    .s4-firm .pillars, .s11 .team-grid, .s12 .phases { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .s4-firm .pillar + .pillar, .s11 .team-member + .team-member { border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(196,163,89,0.1); }
    .s5-client .client-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .s10 .cases { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
    .slide-footer { left: 24px; right: 24px; }
    .horizon { bottom: 50px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="deck">

<!-- ═══ LOGO MACRO — reused in every footer ═══ -->
<!-- Small muted gem: 14x19 -->

<!-- ══════════════════ SLIDE 1: TITLE ══════════════════ -->
<div class="slide s1">
  <div class="starfield"></div>
  <div class="content">
    <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:20px;">Internal Pitch · Confidential</div>
    <div class="title-logo-wrap">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 120 160" width="72" height="96" style="opacity:0.92;">
        <rect x="10" y="8" width="100" height="144" fill="none" stroke="#c4a359" stroke-width="7"/>
        <polygon points="60,20 90,50 100,80 90,110 60,140 30,110 20,80 30,50" fill="#c4a359"/>
        <polygon points="60,38 78,54 78,106 60,122 42,106 42,54" fill="#07111f"/>
        <line x1="60" y1="38" x2="60" y2="20" stroke="#07111f" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="78" y1="54" x2="90" y2="50" stroke="#07111f" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="78" y1="54" x2="100" y2="80" stroke="#07111f" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="78" y1="106" x2="90" y2="110" stroke="#07111f" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="78" y1="106" x2="100" y2="80" stroke="#07111f" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="60" y1="122" x2="60" y2="140" stroke="#07111f" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="42" y1="106" x2="30" y2="110" stroke="#07111f" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="42" y1="106" x2="20" y2="80" stroke="#07111f" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="42" y1="54" x2="30" y2="50" stroke="#07111f" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="42" y1="54" x2="20" y2="80" stroke="#07111f" stroke-width="1.4"/>
      </svg>
      <h1><span class="gold">Earendil</span> Advisory</h1>
    </div>
    <p class="subtitle">A tax firm built to last — not to file</p>
  </div>
  <div class="horizon"></div>
  <div class="slide-footer">
    <span>Confidential</span>
    <span>01 / 13</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════ SLIDE 2: THE MYTH ══════════════════ -->
<div class="slide s2-myth">
  <div class="content">
    <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:24px;">The Founding Myth</div>
    <h2>A mariner who sailed<br>where no mortal<br><span class="gold">had gone before.</span></h2>
    <p class="myth-body" style="margin-top:20px;">
      Eärendil is a character from Tolkien's <em>The Silmarillion</em>. He built a ship and sailed to Valinor — a voyage forbidden to mortals — to petition the Valar on behalf of both Men and Elves during their darkest hour. He arrived before the catastrophe became unrecoverable. He carried the Silmaril on his brow as proof of his purpose. The Valar answered.
    </p>
    <div class="myth-quote" style="margin-top:20px;">
      He goes where others won't. He acts before it's too late.<br>
      He advocates for those who couldn't make the journey themselves.
    </div>
    <p class="myth-body" style="margin-top:20px; font-size:13px;">
      This is not decoration. It is the operating philosophy of the firm. We do not wait for April. We voyage throughout the year so that by the time the moment arrives, the outcome is already determined.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="horizon"></div>
  <div class="slide-footer">
    <div class="footer-logo">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 120 160" width="14" height="19" style="opacity:0.5;">
        <rect x="10" y="8" width="100" height="144" fill="none" stroke="#8a9ab5" stroke-width="7"/>
        <polygon points="60,20 90,50 100,80 90,110 60,140 30,110 20,80 30,50" fill="#8a9ab5"/>
        <polygon points="60,38 78,54 78,106 60,122 42,106 42,54" fill="#0a1628"/>
        <line x1="60" y1="38" x2="60" y2="20" stroke="#0a1628" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="78" y1="54" x2="100" y2="80" stroke="#0a1628" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="78" y1="106" x2="100" y2="80" stroke="#0a1628" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="60" y1="122" x2="60" y2="140" stroke="#0a1628" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="42" y1="106" x2="20" y2="80" stroke="#0a1628" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="42" y1="54" x2="20" y2="80" stroke="#0a1628" stroke-width="1.4"/>
      </svg>
      Earendil Advisory
    </div>
    <span>02 / 13</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════ SLIDE 3: PREMISE ══════════════════ -->
<div class="slide s3">
  <div class="content">
    <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:24px;">The Premise</div>
    <h2>Most tax firms are Zero to Zero.<br><span class="gold italic">We do not have to be.</span></h2>
    <p style="margin-top:16px;">Every CPA shop in Dallas runs the same cycle: client calls in March, we reconstruct the year, we file, we wait. The work is real. The relationship is shallow. Another firm quotes lower next year and wins.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:12px; color:var(--muted);">This is not a pitch to build another compliance shop. It is a pitch to build a firm that accumulates structural advantages over time — through the way we work — and becomes permanently harder to replace.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="horizon"></div>
